{"tid":424143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：適時披露外部勢力參與「佔中」證據","createTime":"2017-10-04T12:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T18:05:57.000Z","uid":36238,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8a96c9b400dab32dcca782b273acb21410281743","tid":424143,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T12:34:14.000Z","msg":"新華網香港10月21日電（記者蘇曉）香港特區行政長官梁振英21日表示，「占中」有外部勢力參與的講法並不是猜測，將在適當時候作適當考慮以決定會否披露證據。<br />\n<br />\n　　 梁振英21日上午出席行政會議前會見傳媒時表示，香港作為中國一部分，同時亦是一個高度開放的城市，一直以來，香港所處的國際環境相當複雜，香港社會對這個問題有一定認知。<br />\n<br />\n　　 梁振英說，早前在訪談節目中說過，「在『占中』這個問題上是有外部勢力參與的」，這個講法並不是猜測，作為政府的負責人，他有責任知道這些事情。<br />\n<br />\n　　 至於是否要公開這些證據，梁振英說，相信任何一個政府在知道這些事情時，都要面對、都要處理。至於應該怎樣披露，或是把這些證據拿出來，「我看在適當時候，我們會作適當考慮。」<br />\n<br />\n　　 對於特區政府與學聯代表即將就政改問題展開對話，梁振英表示，相信市民大眾歡迎政府能夠和學聯代表就政改問題展開對話，一次對話未必能夠解決所有問題，但能夠對話畢竟是一個好的開始。<br />\n<br />\n　　 他說，香港是一個法治社會，在政改問題上，我們一定要跟從基本法和人大常委會有關的決定去落實。特區政府和社會大眾都要務實，在對話的過程當中，討論、探索一些在基本法裏面沒有的規定，或者不符合基本法的一些要求，是不能夠讓我們在2017年達致行政長官普選的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.takungpao.com.hk/hkol/politics/2014-10/2794171.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.takungpao.com.hk%2Fhkol%2Fpolitics%2F2014-10%2F2794171.html&d=RL%2F4GsenS2qWDYAFVAcYZ5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=b918c815\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.takungpao.com.hk/hkol/politics/2014-10/2794171.html</a>"},{"pid":"e07c92206883b32914512bfa843b38cfe1de6a2e","tid":424143,"uid":33307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T12:34:55.000Z","msg":"bin"},{"pid":"b5a603590c699eafa0f12146dfa06d7d784e1dd1","tid":424143,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T12:36:08.000Z","msg":"好似講左用匯豐銀行就係證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b323ca0f2994a844ff01d66d36d8fea06b2faca7","tid":424143,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T12:36:44.000Z","msg":"但阿里巴巴幫加泰人獨立係鐵一般既証據"},{"pid":"aab7a07314fbc05185ed63ba9f59bb056c68faf5","tid":424143,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T12:46:29.000Z","msg":"屈臣氏支持佔中"},{"pid":"2a7bf1a02f359449042cb69d4d0f9ff1bb0cec58","tid":424143,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:42:50.000Z","msg":"香港政府支持佔中 大部分佔中人士仍然係香港本地合法居民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b905481df9ca97962ef0a2d044ee34d26f237f","tid":424143,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:47:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7f15c84c8512d561ea6371b8514f26b1a57f0c","tid":424143,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:49:00.000Z","msg":"公布咗啦，咪澳洲UGL囉"},{"pid":"013e1248125be780aa189eb07139f605ce8ca3f0","tid":424143,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:50:22.000Z","msg":"結果佢做完嗰日都未披露過出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61b5f268a3ce3e2392ba1215a894ef1aeb72933","tid":424143,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:50:55.000Z","msg":"證明成件事根本係佢自己作出嚟"},{"pid":"f24ceff93f60cba4c150290fddbf3c4e6a8eb052","tid":424143,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T14:24:47.000Z","msg":"UGL的犯罪事件，幾時可以調查？！"},{"pid":"a902645d13e871acf5eea06b66d62cced1e9f4cd","tid":424143,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T18:04:45.000Z","msg":"根本就9up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1866245a48cde25038fe7936e63cc4445c80dd","tid":424143,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T18:05:57.000Z","msg":"on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}